snippet.title: FIFA 21 | Next Level Speed (PS5, Xbox Series X|S)
snippet.description:
Next Level Speed in FIFA 21 on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S gets you from menu to match in under two seconds. FIFA 21 launches December 4 on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S: http://x.ea.com/66398 

Entitle for FIFA 21 on either PlayStation 4 or Xbox One before the release of FIFA 22, and upgrade your game for the equivalent next generation console (PlayStation 5 or Xbox Series X|S) for free.* All progress you make and content you acquire in FIFA 21 Ultimate Team and VOLTA FOOTBALL will carry over!** http://x.ea.com/66389

Get FIFA 21 now! http://x.ea.com/66390

Subscribe to see more FIFA 21 videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

#FIFA21 #FeelNextLevel
